Package app.dao

Class GenericHibernateDao<T extends java.io.Serializable>

java.lang.Object
app.dao.GenericHibernateDao<T>
Type Parameters:
T - Class of Dao's entity.
All Implemented Interfaces:
IGenericDao<T>
public class GenericHibernateDao<T extends java.io.Serializable>
extends java.lang.Object
implements IGenericDao<T>
Class that implements Data Access Object. It uses generic parameters so it can be easily reproduced and implemented. It is the lowest layer of application architecture that is used to interact with database.
